  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter in a large pot over medium heat until melted.",
    "Add diced onion and sliced carrots, sauté until onion translucent.",
    "Stir in diced potatoes and cook for 5 minutes, letting them soften slightly.",
    "Pour in white wine, fish stock, and kombu cold extract, bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Season with chilli powder, salt & pepper, and reduce heat to low.",
    "Add cod fillets, cover, and simmer for 10 minutes, until fish is opaque and flakes easily.",
    "Stir in fresh dill and lemon juice, adjust seasoning if needed.",
    "Serve hot with crusty bread, enjoying the winey, cozy flavors."
  ],
